    17вҶ’	// false or true based on the stdout's file descriptor referring to a terminal
    18вҶ’	// or not. It's also set to true if the NO_COLOR environment variable is
    19вҶ’	// set (regardless of its value). This is a global option and affects all
    20вҶ’	// colors. For more control over each color block use the methods
    21вҶ’	// DisableColor() individually.
    22вҶ’	NoColor = noColorIsSet() || os.Getenv("TERM") == "dumb" ||
